<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عنِ المُغيرَةِ بنِ زِيادٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٧٩٤٦]</span> عُمرُ بنُ أَنسِ بنِ مالِكٍ الأَنْصارِيُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَمَّا كَبِرَ أَنسٌ، أَطْعمَ وَأَفْطرَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوى عَنهُ حُميْدٌ الطَّويلُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٧٩٤٧]</span> عُمرُ الأَبَحُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عنِ ابنِ أَبي عَروبَةَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سَمعَ مِنهُ خَليلُ بنُ عُمرَ بنِ إِبْراهيمَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مُنكَرُ الحَديثِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
